# is-alphabet Checks whether passed string contains alphabets, digits and vocabulory. ## Installation ```bash npm i is-alphabet --save ``` ## Usage ```js const isAlpha = require('is-alphabet'); if(isAlpha('Some string with english alphabets')) { console.log('pure english'); } ``` ## Development ```bash npm i npm test ``` #### Contributors | [![Divjot Singh](https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/bogas04?s=100)
